name: Cross Trainer Double
description: A durable outdoor cross trainer designed for two users, perfect for improving cardiovascular fitness, coordination, and endurance. Built with weather-resistant materials for long-lasting performance in open gyms and parks.

name: Bicycle
description: An outdoor stationary bike for a full lower-body workout. Ideal for enhancing leg strength, stamina, and cardiovascular health. Features a sturdy frame and ergonomic design for comfortable use.

name: Elliptical Double
description: Dual-user elliptical trainer providing a smooth, joint-friendly motion for cardio exercise. Great for improving heart health, burning calories, and strengthening muscles in both upper and lower body.

name: Sit & Stand Twister
description: Versatile twister station for engaging the core muscles while standing or sitting. Helps improve flexibility, balance, and abdominal strength. Suitable for all age groups in public fitness areas.

name: Knee Hip Raise
description: An effective outdoor fitness station for strengthening abdominal muscles, hip flexors, and core stability. Built for long-term use in outdoor environments.

name: Pull-Up Rack
description: Heavy-duty pull-up rack designed for bodyweight training. Ideal for building upper body strength, endurance, and grip power. Supports a variety of pull-up and chin-up variations.

name: Exercising Up Bar
description: Multi-purpose upper body exercise bar for pull-ups, chin-ups, and hanging exercises. Perfect for developing arms, shoulders, chest, and back muscles.

name: Riding Trainer Double
description: Dual-rider outdoor trainer that simulates cycling motion. Enhances cardiovascular endurance, leg strength, and coordination for two users simultaneously.

name: Triple Twister
description: Three-station waist twister for group workouts. Improves flexibility, balance, and core strength while encouraging social interaction in outdoor gyms.

name: Pull Chair Double
description: Double-user pull chair machine for developing arm, shoulder, and chest muscles. Designed for smooth resistance and long-term durability.

name: Rowing Machine
description: Outdoor rowing station for a full-body workout targeting arms, back, core, and legs. Excellent for improving endurance and overall fitness.

name: Abdominal Exerciser
description: Specialized equipment for toning and strengthening abdominal muscles. Supports core stability and posture improvement.

name: Butterfly/Pec-Dec Chest Expander
description: Dual-function chest expander for targeting chest, shoulders, and upper arms. Supports both butterfly and pec-dec movements for versatile training.

name: Chest Press
description: Sturdy outdoor chest press machine for building pectoral, shoulder, and triceps strength. Smooth resistance mechanism for effective workouts.

name: Weight Lifting Trainer
description: Outdoor strength training station for lifting and pressing exercises. Ideal for building muscle mass and overall body strength.
